That's it. That's your Sheriff's Office.

00:11:14.122 --> 00:11:15.422
These guys are everywhere.

00:11:17.877 --> 00:11:22.410
So the city of Okeechobee comes right up to
the shore of Lake Okeechobee,

00:11:22.410 --> 00:11:24.009
and not far from here

00:11:24.010 --> 00:11:28.202
was the largest disaster
in Florida State history.

00:11:28.497 --> 00:11:32.151
Over 2,500 people died in 1928.

00:11:32.340 --> 00:11:33.838
When the hurricane happened.

00:11:33.838 --> 00:11:37.225
The great, I believe it's called
the Okeechobee Hurricane.

00:11:37.845 --> 00:11:40.385
The biggest one to date
as far as casualties.

00:11:40.769 --> 00:11:43.258
And right after
they built this dike system.

00:11:43.258 --> 00:11:47.069
It runs the whole perimeter of the lake.

00:11:47.429 --> 00:11:52.246
It totally changed
the southern interior part of Florida.

00:11:52.246 --> 00:11:54.867
This is an integral part of the Everglades.

00:11:54.867 --> 00:11:59.001
It used to take roughly a year
for water to get from the south side here,

00:11:59.654 --> 00:12:01.248
all the way out to the gulf.

00:12:01.668 --> 00:12:03.093
Because all the dikes,

00:12:03.620 --> 00:12:06.032
and the modern infrastructure
put into Florida.

00:12:06.032 --> 00:12:07.139
That's all changed.

00:12:07.532 --> 00:12:12.003
We're going to get south on the south side
here into the town of Clewiston.

00:12:12.010 --> 00:12:14.495
And Clewiston is known for sugar.

00:12:14.495 --> 00:12:17.925
The sweetest city in America they say.

00:12:18.264 --> 00:12:21.193
And the sugar industry
has benefited greatly

00:12:21.193 --> 00:12:24.539
from the taming of Lake Okeechobee.

00:12:25.511 --> 00:12:26.511
[country music]

00:12:58.538 --> 00:12:59.645
Check this out guys.

00:12:59.645 --> 00:13:01.666
