00:13:01.939 --> 00:13:03.147
The street patterns.

00:13:03.577 --> 00:13:05.314
Everything seems to be named sugar.

00:13:05.314 --> 00:13:08.433
Sugar Park, Sugar Drive,
sugar this, sugar that.

00:13:09.266 --> 00:13:11.954
Once the dike was put in
the irrigation was controlled.

00:13:12.187 --> 00:13:13.457
The flooding was controlled.

00:13:13.726 --> 00:13:16.152
Just prime territory for sugar cane.

00:13:16.598 --> 00:13:18.238
So as you saw coming into town.

00:13:18.678 --> 00:13:21.700
Just sugar cane fields
for as far as the eye could see.

00:13:22.030 --> 00:13:26.460
This is ground zero for sugar in America.

00:13:26.460 --> 00:13:31.129
Florida is the biggest sugar producer,
US Sugar, the biggest sugar company.

00:13:31.590 --> 00:13:33.489
Most of this stays domestic.

00:13:34.660 --> 00:13:36.042
A bit goes international.

00:13:36.042 --> 00:13:38.341
But most domestic from my understanding.

00:13:39.155 --> 00:13:42.391
And so you are tied into this town.

00:13:42.977 --> 00:13:45.152
If you're eating sugar
which most of us are.

00:13:45.652 --> 00:13:48.672
And sugar as we know can be found
in bread and pretty much everything.

00:13:49.462 --> 00:13:52.508
Then Clewiston is the starting point

00:13:52.982 --> 00:13:55.714
for the food you eat many a times.

00:13:55.721 --> 00:13:58.386
You're drinking a soda today,
having a candy bar.

00:13:59.119 --> 00:14:00.642
